<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200811/f307abcb26df48b69e4ca84c3cdf91fe.png" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200811/cb6017935daa4a36ae204a460874569a.png" /></p>
<p>杰维•辛格：我们的设备由一个计算机的中央盒子和像这样放在你手臂上的手臂带组成。手臂带内装有电动机，计算机和内部摄像头。计算机能通过你的手机响应。当你对着手机说：“嘿，克里斯蒂”，设备会开始工作并使用摄像头拍照。相机能看到周围的世界，并了解正在发生的事情。然后计算机会在耳边告诉他们：“这是一部个人电话。这是一瓶水。”</p>
<p>Jaiveer Singh: Our device is composed of a central box from the computer and an armband that goes on your arm like this. The armband has motors, a computer and camera inside this device. The computer is able to respond to your phone. When you say ‘Hey Christy’ into your phone, the cleaner works on and starts taking a picture with the camera. The camera will see the world around the person and figure what’s going on. Then the computer will tell the person in their ear "This is a personal phone. This is a water bottle."</p>
<p>最后，杰维为他们的参赛展示做出了总结。</p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200811/9fedfb5d526849cab3c0397a7467b1aa.png" /></p>
<p>杰维•辛格：在面试中，我觉得一开始我的表现有点不稳定。但我认为我们总体上做得很好。我认为我们的产品是一个非常好的产品，事实上它有潜力让很多人的生活变得更好，我们有很大的机会可以让大家都了解到这一点，我希望他们能理解我们的使命和目标，那就是让世界变得更美好。</p>
<p>Jaiveer Singh: Based on the interview, I think I went on a little bit rocky at first. But I think we did a pretty good job overall. I think I went on a little bit rocky at first. But I think we did a pretty good job overall. For the final result, I am hoping we get to move on the second round, and we will find out in around two hours. But I think that our product is a very good product and has the potential to the make a lot of people’s lives very much better and I think that because that, we have a pretty strong chance to recognize that and I hope they will understand our mission and our objective to make the world a better place.</p>
